sentences: Jennifer Carole Ledger (born 8 December 1989) is an English singer, drummer and co-vocalist for the American Christian rock band Skillet.
Ledger released a solo EP in 2018 under the name Ledger.
She played drums in a local band and was a finalist for the United Kingdom Drummer of the Year competition in 2006.

She has been Skillet's drummer and female vocalist since 2008, beginning with their promotional tour for the album Comatose.
Ledger stated that she and bandmate Korey Cooper began to write music for her own pop-influenced solo-project album in about 2012.
In March 2018, it was announced that her debut EP, Ledger, was scheduled to be released on 13 April.
